A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Atlanta Postal Credit Union upon its 100th anniversary; and
2 for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, this year, Atlanta Postal Credit Union (APCU) will celebrate the grand occasion
4 of its 100th anniversary, representing a century of dedicated service to postal workers, their
5 families, and the broader community; and
6 WHEREAS, founded in 1925, APCU holds the distinction of being the first credit union
7 chartered in the State of Georgia, laying the foundation for a long-standing legacy of
8 financial inclusion and empowerment; and
9 WHEREAS, over the course of 100 years, APCU has grown from its modest beginnings into
10 one of Georgia's most respected and impactful financial institutions, remaining committed
11 to the credit union mission of People Helping People; and
12 WHEREAS, APCU has consistently provided exceptional financial products and services,
13 helping its members achieve financial goals, plan for their futures, and support their families
14 across generations; and
