15 WHEREAS, through its unwavering dedication to innovation, APCU has adapted to the
16 changing needs of its members by embracing technological advancements while maintaining
17 a strong tradition of personalized service; and
18 WHEREAS, deeply rooted in community values, APCU has demonstrated outstanding civic
19 leadership by supporting charitable causes, promoting financial literacy, and investing in the
20 well-being of the communities it serves; and
21 WHEREAS, this centennial milestone reflects APCU's lasting impact on the financial
22 well-being of individuals and families throughout Georgia and beyond as well as its
23 continued role as a pillar of trust, service, and stability.
24 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
25 recognize and commend Atlanta Postal Credit Union upon its 100th anniversary and extend
26 best wishes for continued success.
27 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
28 to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to Atlanta Postal
29 Credit Union.
